lead_paragraph: Brice Johnson had 17 points and 11 rebounds, and No. 2 North Carolina beat Boston College 89-62 on Saturday for its 12th straight win.

headline.print_headline: Johnson Leads No. 2 UNC to 12th Straight Win, 89-62 Over BC
